<br>
If you really want to see a good increase on your gold and silver, tradeskills are the way to go.  I recently switched to consignments from powerskilling tradeskills (very effective for skill increase but terribly hard on the pocketbook) and since I've been doing consignments, my skill went up 100 pts and made approx 18 gold in 2 days.  Not to mention I can also outfit myself and all my friends with decent armor. <p><CENTER>
