<br>
Further south are the Sheeries and even further south are the silvermine badgers, rock people and ludic????s.  Best to bind in Argath and swim over when you are this far south.  <br>
<br>
At 1 Gold per 10 kills, it does not take long to build up the kitty.<br>
<br>
